description:
The easiest way to upgrade your system into wireless N network. 
Connect your PC/NB to a wireless network in minutes using high speed USB2.0 interface. 
12x speed and 4x coverage over wireless G . 
802.11b/g/n 2.0 provide further coverage, less dead spot and higher throughput. 
MIMO technology throughput up to 300 Mbps for Ralink 2T2R solution. 
Supports MIMO technology with 2 Built-in Internal Printed Antennas 
Easy setup with Wi-Fi Protected Setup (WPS). 
Security support WPA/WPA2 (AES, 64,128-WEP with shared-key authentication). 
Support Cisco CCS V1.0, V2.0 and V3.0 compliant WPS. 
Wireless Multimedia Enhancements Quality of Service support (QoS) / enhanced power saving for Dynamic Networking 
RNX-N1 is also fully compatible with IEEE 802.11b/g standard. 
Compatible with Windows 2000, XP, Vista 32 and 64 bit/ MAC 10.3/ 10.4/ 10.5/10.6
LED indicator for Power/Link 
Advanced power management for Low power consumption

NOTICE: RNX-N1 doesn't support Linux now.
title: Rosewill RNX-N1 Wireless-N 2.0 Dongle 02.11b/g/n USB2.0
